# CI After Push

- Workflow/module changes should have stub-run coverage through module wrappers, workflow smoke tests, or `scripts/ci/run_nextflow_smoke_tests.sh`.
- Docs changes should keep docs generation and `mkdocs build --strict` green.
- MCP server changes should build the TypeScript package and keep Python integration/e2e expectations current.
- When CI coverage is intentionally incomplete, record the gap in handoff/state.
